## The Bifurcation of Digital Existence: Exploring User Space and Kernel Space

"Kernel space" and "User space" redirect here. For the mathematical definition, one might seek solace in the abstract realm of a [Null space](/Null_space), where vectors vanish into nothingness, much like my enthusiasm for explaining basic computing concepts. For the more mundane, self-referential user space on Wikipedia, you'll find it under [Wikipedia:User pages](/Wikipedia:User_pages).

